title: GORGEOUS 2 BED/2.5 TOWNHOME W/CARPORT AVAIL EARLY AUGUST
posting_body: ['Luxury 2 bed/2.5 bath town home available early August.', 'The residence is 1465 sq ft with modern appliances, new carpeting, new paint, beautifully glazed counter tops in kitchen & baths, washer/dryer hook up, private entrance, balcony and carport.', 'Utilities are not included, it is gas heat, hot water & gas cooking.', 'This 20 unit community is within 1 mile of 93, 95 & Rt 3, several shopping malls, movie theaters and numerous fine dining establishments.', 'Enjoy all the conveniences of city living while residing in a suburban neighborhood.', 'Community boasts full amenities including a large swimming pool & wading pool, fitness center, tennis court, play ground and barbecue area.', 'Please reply or call 781-933-1247 for further information and a time to view.', 'Tours are by appointment only at this time.', 'Call now!', 'this most desirable town home is not going to last, a rare availability at this community.', 'For more information and directions, please visit <URL>.', 'Sorry, NO PETS.']
